edu.vccs.vdh275.math

Class Cal

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.vccs.vdh275.math.Cal

  • public class Cal
extends java.lang.Object
    Use this class to calculate different operations for two numbers
    Example:
    Cal.add(2,1);
    This will return 3.0 as the sum between these two numbers.
    Author:
    Vanessa Harris
